Class Cinema

  • Object
    • Cinema

  • public class Cinema
extends Object
    Represents a cinema in the cineplex Contains information of class of this cinema and cinema code of this cinema and seats in this cinema and cinema index of this cinema and number of empty seats in this cinema and number of rows of seats in this cinema and number of columes of seats in this cinema cinema can show different movies
    Author:
    SSP2 Team 1
